textBox.richText: On set of the Moogy Bruise Preopic

Damn, it feels good to be a gangster. The above shot is from the set of my new short film, aka my living room. I’m calling the movie a Moogy Bruise Preopic because it’s a biopic about Moogy that tells his pre-op story. I love living with Alex and Andrew. Thanks for encouraging me, gentlemen. http://www.dubstep.fm/ http://www.audiocodone.com/ http://splatinum.bandcamp.com/
